---
title: Bacon & Broccoli Penne with Parmesan, Sour Cream & Chives
description: Florets of broccoli and crispy bacon may not be the first combo you think of when it comes to pasta, but you can trust us on this
one! Mix it all into a moreish sour cream-based sauce for a flavour explosion that's even worthy of Nonna's picky palate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-broccoli-penne-a06490ee.jpg
